	I, ${Name}, understand that I will be supervised by the Harris County Community Supervision and Corrections Department as a courtesy to my original supervisory authority and to myself.  I further understand that I am obligated to fully comply with the following requirements in order to retain the privilege of having my supervision supervised by the Harris County Community Supervision and Corrections Department.





		_foreach_(eachCondition ${conditions} 'even' 'odd')

				${eachCondition.conditionNumber}
				${eachCondition.conditionName}


				_foreach_(subCondition ${eachCondition.subConditions} 'even' 'odd')


						${subCondition.subConditionNumber}
						${subCondition.subConditionName}

				_endfor_

		_endfor_






		I understand that my failure to comply with the above requirements may result in the return of my supervision to the original supervisory authority.  I also understand that my supervision may be returned to the original supervisory authority if I am uncooperative in any manner with my Harris County Community Supervision Officer.




